First off, the Cold Dark _is_ up now (sorry)

I just munged the heirarchy a little, flipping $person and $player.  I globally
changed $player to $user (_everything_ which referenced $player, or player is
now changed to $user or user).  I created $player under $person.  $person will
have all 'physical' attributes on it, $player will have RPG stuff on it.  here
is how it is right now:

Descendants of User:
User  &lt;$user&gt; (MI)
  Person  &lt;$person&gt;
    *Player  &lt;$player&gt;
      *Builder  &lt;$builder&gt;
        *Hacker  &lt;$programmer&gt;

